Promotional Terms

Earn 2X points on any purchase made from 08/11/2024 12:01 AM PDT until 08/11/2024 11:59 PM PDT. Limit one-time use per customer within the promotional period. Must have an account to receive rewards points. Must be signed into account. Offer not applicable with recurring orders or e-gift cards. Points can be combined with other Thrive Causemetics promos. Points are not earned on returned products. **See Thrive Causemetics Rewards Terms & FAQ on our website for more details on our Rewards Program**
